  <sect2 role="installation">
    <title>Installation of xdotool</title>

<!-- Not needed with 4.20260303.1
    <para>
      First, fix an invalid path in an installed pkg-config file:
    </para>

<screen><userinput>sed -i 's#/local##' libxdo.pc</userinput></screen>
-->

    <para>
      Install <application>xdotool</application> by running the following
      commands:
    </para>

<screen><userinput>make WITHOUT_RPATH_FIX=1</userinput></screen>

    <para>
      To run the tests, do:
    </para>

<screen remap='test'><userinput>cd t
make all-headless
cd ..</userinput></screen>

    <para>
      Now, as the &root; user:
    </para>

<screen role="root"><userinput>make PREFIX=/usr INSTALLMAN=/usr/share/man install</userinput></screen>

  </sect2>

